{"tid":2430293,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲偵察機罕現東海　一周前始部署至沖繩嘉手納基地","createTime":"2021-03-03T00:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T11:36:40.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5b61840c0a22a2baaa72a4e6cc213e07777f443a","tid":2430293,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T00:01:31.000Z","msg":"澳洲偵察機罕現東海　一周前始部署至沖繩嘉手納基地 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20210302/s00004/1614680655628/%e6%be%b3%e6%b4%b2%e5%81%b5%e5%af%9f%e6%a9%9f%e7%bd%95%e7%8f%be%e6%9d%b1%e6%b5%b7-%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e5%89%8d%e5%a7%8b%e9%83%a8%e7%bd%b2%e8%87%b3%e6%b2%96%e7%b9%a9%e5%98%89%e6%89%8b%e7%b4%8d%e5%9f%ba%e5%9c%b0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20210302%2Fs00004%2F1614680655628%2F%25e6%25be%25b3%25e6%25b4%25b2%25e5%2581%25b5%25e5%25af%259f%25e6%25a9%259f%25e7%25bd%2595%25e7%258f%25be%25e6%259d%25b1%25e6%25b5%25b7-%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%2591%25a8%25e5%2589%258d%25e5%25a7%258b%25e9%2583%25a8%25e7%25bd%25b2%25e8%2587%25b3%25e6%25b2%2596%25e7%25b9%25a9%25e5%2598%2589%25e6%2589%258b%25e7%25b4%258d%25e5%259f%25ba%25e5%259c%25b0&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiuqnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=f5aefd52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20210302%2Fs00004%2F1614680655628%2F%25e6%25be%25b3%25e6%25b4%25b2%25e5%2581%25b5%25e5%25af%259f%25e6%25a9%259f%25e7%25bd%2595%25e7%258f%25be%25e6%259d%25b1%25e6%25b5%25b7-%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%2591%25a8%25e5%2589%258d%25e5%25a7%258b%25e9%2583%25a8%25e7%25bd%25b2%25e8%2587%25b3%25e6%25b2%2596%25e7%25b9%25a9%25e5%2598%2589%25e6%2589%258b%25e7%25b4%258d%25e5%259f%25ba%25e5%259c%25b0&h=5e22631a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20210302/s00004/1614680655628/%e6%be%b3%e6%b4%b2%e5%81%b5%e5%af%9f%e6%a9%9f%e7%bd%95%e7%8f%be%e6%9d%b1%e6%b5%b7-%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e5%89%8d%e5%a7%8b%e9%83%a8%e7%bd%b2%e8%87%b3%e6%b2%96%e7%b9%a9%e5%98%89%e6%89%8b%e7%b4%8d%e5%9f%ba%e5%9c%b0</a><br />\n<br />\n「南海戰略態勢感知」平台發布消息指出，今日（2日）上午，澳洲空軍一架P-8A反潛巡邏機進入東海空域活動。這是該機自2月25日從澳洲部署至日本沖繩嘉手納基地以來的首次行動，其目的有待進一步觀察。<br />\n<br />\n此前在東海、南海上空活動的偵察機、巡邏機大多來自美國，澳洲偵察機出現在東海的情況十分罕見。從部署時間和地點上看，這架澳洲反潛巡邏機是為執行多國聯合監視任務而部署到日本沖繩。<br />\n<br />\n美國「空軍技術」網站曾在2月25日報道稱，澳洲國防部當天宣布向日本部署一架澳洲皇家空軍的P-8A反潛巡邏機，用於執行代號為「阿爾戈斯」（ARGOS）的行動任務，這架巡邏機將部署在日本沖繩嘉手納基地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「阿爾戈斯」行動於2018年啟動，旨在應對非法貿易和逃避制裁的問題，參與行動的國家包括美國、加拿大、法國、日本、英國和新西蘭。自行動開始以來，澳洲就部署了一架海上巡邏機和一艘護衛艦來支持這一行動。"},{"pid":"5ae28c02fc9d666aed30fc154416c087fb15876a","tid":2430293,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T00:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754a6f83df1cecabcbd3fcd127d771bc027067bd","tid":2430293,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T00:49:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78b8db311d85b7e7727027a12c9fc1a753f618f","tid":2430293,"uid":289459,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5b61840c0a22a2baaa72a4e6cc213e07777f443a","tid":2430293,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T00:01:31.000Z","msg":"澳洲偵察機罕現東海　一周前始部署至沖繩嘉手納基地 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20210302/s00004/1614680655628/%e6%be%b3%e6%b4%b2%e5%81%b5%e5%af%9f%e6%a9%9f%e7%bd%95%e7%8f%be%e6%9d%b1%e6%b5%b7-%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e5%89%8d%e5%a7%8b%e9%83%a8%e7%bd%b2%e8%87%b3%e6%b2%96%e7%b9%a9%e5%98%89%e6%89%8b%e7%b4%8d%e5%9f%ba%e5%9c%b0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.co